article_title: Georgia and Tennessee downgraded in CNBC ranking of business strength

article_metadata.description: Georgia, which CNBC ranked No. 1 for business competitiveness in 2014, fell to No. 6. Tennessee, which ranked No. 14 in 2014, declined to No. 17. Alabama ranked 41st.
